text: Would like to compliment Staff Ms Cindy for her positive and friendly service towards customers. Our usual place for groceries and have seen Ms Cindy on duties as Cashier at the cashier counter and/or at Self-pay corner. She has always demonstrated patience and willingness to help customers with a positive vibe despite the crowd. Thank you Ms Cindy, you always make our shopping experience at Giant very pleasant!  Very hard to find such good services nowadays. Hope management will continue to keep and reward such good staff ! Thank you.
Always open. Always has deals and everything is a giant here. Nice place for shopping. Highly recommended
My go to supermarket in the east.
